  <!-- Section: Application Process -->
  <section id="application" class="scroll-mt-24 mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">Application Process</h2>

    <p class="mb-4">
      When the IIP is active, applications are submitted to Immigration Service Delivery (ISD, formerly INIS) in Dublin. The process involves pre-approval, investment completion, and then residence permit issuance. Here's the typical timeline and steps.
    </p>

    <ComparisonTable columns={timelineColumns} rows={timelineRows} />

    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 mt-8 mb-3">Step-by-Step Guide</h3>

    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-primary-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">1</div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900">Engage Professional Advisors</h4>
          <p class="text-neutral-600">Hire an Irish immigration lawyer and financial advisor familiar with the IIP. They'll assess your eligibility, recommend the best investment route, and guide documentation. Essential for first-time applicants—the process is complex and errors cause delays.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-primary-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">2</div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900">Document Source of Funds</h4>
          <p class="text-neutral-600">Prepare comprehensive documentation of your €2M+ net worth and the source of your investment funds. This includes audited accounts, tax returns, property valuations, and transaction histories. Expect this to take 1-2 months if records aren't already organized.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-primary-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">3</div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900">Select Investment Vehicle</h4>
          <p class="text-neutral-600">Choose between enterprise investment, approved fund, REIT, or endowment. If using a fund, select from the list of approved funds. Sign preliminary agreements but do not transfer funds yet—investment is made after approval.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-primary-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">4</div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900">Arrange Health Insurance</h4>
          <p class="text-neutral-600">Secure private health insurance covering you and your dependents in Ireland. Obtain confirmation letter from the insurer for your application. Coverage must be active from the date you receive your residence permit.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-primary-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">5</div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900">Submit IIP Application</h4>
          <p class="text-neutral-600">Submit your complete application to Immigration Service Delivery with all supporting documents. Pay the €1,500 application fee. Applications are typically submitted during specific evaluation windows (when programme is active).</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-primary-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">6</div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900">Due Diligence and Review</h4>
          <p class="text-neutral-600">Immigration conducts background checks and reviews your application. This typically takes 4-6 months. You may be asked for additional documentation or clarification. The evaluation committee meets periodically to review applications.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-primary-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">7</div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900">Receive Approval and Complete Investment</h4>
          <p class="text-neutral-600">Upon approval, you have 90 days to complete your investment. Transfer funds to the approved enterprise, fund, or REIT. For endowments, complete the donation. Obtain proof of investment completion.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-primary-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">8</div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900">Register and Receive Residence Permit</h4>
          <p class="text-neutral-600">Travel to Dublin to register with the Garda National Immigration Bureau (GNIB). Receive your Irish Residence Permit (IRP) card—Stamp 4 permission. Initial permit valid for 2 years, renewable for 3 years, then 5 years.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-lg p-4 mt-6">
      <p class="text-blue-800">
        <strong>Path to citizenship:</strong> After 5 years of residence (with 1 year continuous residence before application), you can apply for Irish citizenship through naturalization. Irish citizenship grants you an EU passport with visa-free access to 180+ countries and the right to live and work anywhere in the EU.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

